      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROBELL CLYDE (8) finished in the money fresh when third (20.07) at this track in a Free For All. Form here sound including 16 wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Must come into calculations. FRYING BONNIE (1) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 1.75 lengths over 300m Casino in 17.39. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Hard to beat again. CASH IN COLOUR (4) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (24.03) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Casino. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. MEG'S GIRL (7) can sneak into the finish.",
